    "Description": "<p class=\"p3\">The Toronto Vegetarian Association&#39;s Resource Centre is a unique library and bookstore carrying Toronto&rsquo;s largest selection of vegetarian books and cookbooks! It&rsquo;s also a great place for omnivores and vegetarians to stop in for advice and information only&nbsp; making healthier, greener, more compassionate food choices. On top of that, it&rsquo;s run by a dedicated group of volunteers!</p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\"><br />\nWe are looking for more vegetarian* volunteers to staff the Resource Centre twice a month (one Wednesday evening from 6 to 9 pm, one Saturday afternoon from 1 to 4 pm). On Saturdays, you will also record a podcast.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\"><br />\nQualifications:</p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\">*At least one year of experience living on a vegetarian diet (no consumption of fish, seafood, meat, chicken, game, fowl, or other flesh) is required for this position.<br />\nA caring, able researcher will thrive in this position. RC volunteers should have excellent customer service skills, and be able to both work well with others and independently.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\"><br />\nResponsibilities:<br />\nHelping customers sign books in and out; Answering questions in person and via email about vegetarianism; Providing personal perspective and support on vegetarian living; Handling book and membership sales; Assisting with ongoing maintenance of the RC including cataloging new books and magazines; Re-shelving books, occasionally assisting TVA staff with office tasks; From time to time, plan and coordinate events in the RC, such as an annual open house and bake sales.</p>",
    "Website": "http://veg.ca/",
    "Application Instructions": "<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Next Steps: If you&rsquo;re interested in this position, please send your resume and cover letter to Angeline Judge, Resource Centre Chair, at <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><a href=\"mailto:tvarcchair@gmail.com\">tvarcchair@gmail.com</a></span>, with the subject Resource Centre Application.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Visit: <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><a href=\"http://veg.ca\">veg.ca</a></span></span></p>",
    "Logo": "image://v1/7473a8_d0bfa6688fc149a09cfe806d220b5c9c~mv2.jpg/240_255/v-mark%20green.jpg",
    "Featured": "",
    "Viewopptext": "View",
