    "Opportunities (Ref)": "/Opportunities/10035",
    "Commitment": "1.5 hours a week for 12 weeks",
    "Description": "<p class=\"p3\">Are you...</p>\n\n<ul class=\"font_9\">\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">Fun and enthusiastic?</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">Open to other cultures and diversity?</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">At least 21 years old? Committed to making a positive difference?</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">Interested in developing new skills that could improve your own life?</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"p3\">If you answered &quot;yes&quot; to the above, then Kids Now is the right choice for you.</p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\">What&#39;s involved?</p>\n\n<ul class=\"font_9\">\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">One six-hour training session with other mentors</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">Weekly 1.5 hour program sessions for 12 weeks (fall or spring programs)</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p class=\"p3\">Half-hour prep time each week for 12 weeks</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"wixGuard\">​</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p3\">When you become a Volunteer Mentor, you become a positive influence for 1.5 hours per week and you improve your own leadership skills too! Our mentors tell us they not only have a personally rewarding experience as a mentor, but they also develop their own communication &amp; leadership skills that they use in their work environment and personal lives.</p>",
    "Website": "http://www.kidsnowcanada.org/",
    "Application Instructions": "<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">How to sign up:</span></p>\n\n<ul style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n\t<li>\n\t<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Complete and submit the application form <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><a href=\"http://www.kidsnowcanada.org/volunteer/volunteer_application/\">http://www.kidsnowcanada.org/volunteer/volunteer_application/</a></span></span></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Pass a personal reference and police check</span></p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Attend a personal interview with a Kids Now program manager</span></p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>",
